flowchart LR
  DOC[Markdown 文档 + 隐形标签] --> RTM[docs/rtm.json]
  RTM --> OAS[backend/openapi/openapi.yaml]
  RTM --> BDD[tests/specs/*.feature]
  RTM --> NFR[tests/baselines/nonfunctional.json]
  OAS --> CONTRACT[接口合约校验器配置]
  DOC --> INDEX[docs/index/chunks.jsonl]
  RTM --> GRAPH[docs/index/knowledge-graph.json]
  INDEX --> AGENT[检索-生成-验证 Agent]
  GRAPH --> AGENT
  BDD --> CI[一致性 CI Gate]
  CONTRACT --> CI
  NFR --> CI
  CI --> AUDIT[审计智能体差异报告]
  AUDIT --> FIX[主智能体修正/人工仲裁]
